00:26:21.220 --> 00:26:23.860
And I think that
that's really the core

00:26:23.860 --> 00:26:25.410
of the problem is
that lots of brands

00:26:25.410 --> 00:26:27.870
are using the traditional
marketing model of shouting

00:26:27.870 --> 00:26:30.890
at people when what people
want to have is a conversation.

00:26:30.890 --> 00:26:33.720
They want value added
from participating.

00:26:33.720 --> 00:26:35.990
And that value can be
as little as feeling

00:26:35.990 --> 00:26:42.236
like they contributed some
insight to the conversation.

00:26:42.236 --> 00:26:45.107
Does that address
your question at all?

00:26:45.107 --> 00:26:45.690
AUDIENCE: Yes.

